text: Þonne sind þis þa sutulus tan gedere to Beasfeld.
Ærest on norþe weasðan eastrihte of EllenbeorgeXVgirda.
Þan on suðrihte swa Moulman strecte oþ landes ende.
Þonne west be Æwille mearce oþ þone Cwichege suð andlang heges on þane bradan hegewai.
Þonne on Cingdene on abbudes mearce of abbudes mearce eft on Ellenbeorh.
